          <li><a href="#work"><i class="fi fi-rr-exchange mi"></i>Platform Migration</a></li>
        </ul></div>
        <div class="mega-col promo span2">
          <span class="label"><span class="idx"><i class="fi fi-rr-trophy"></i></span> Selected Work</span>
          <h3>Real projects. Measurable impact.</h3>
          <p class="mega-p">Real client results — higher conversion, fewer review hours, faster throughput. Outcomes, not just deliverables.</p>
