    <div class="mega" data-mega="why">
      <div class="wrap mega-grid four">
        <div class="mega-col"><h4>Our Approach</h4><ul>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs#approach`}><i class="fi fi-rr-workflow mi"></i>How We Work</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs#accountability`}><i class="fi fi-rr-shield-check mi"></i>US/EU Accountability Model</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs#accountability`}><i class="fi fi-rr-clock mi"></i>Time Zone-Aligned Delivery</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs#approach`}><i class="fi fi-rr-users mi"></i>Co-Engineering Methodology</a></li>
        </ul></div>
        <div class="mega-col"><h4>Trust &amp; Proof</h4><ul>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs#proof`}><i class="fi fi-rr-comment-quote mi"></i>Client Testimonials</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs#proof`}><i class="fi fi-rr-medal mi"></i>Awards &amp; Recognition</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs#proof`}><i class="fi fi-rr-star mi"></i>Clutch &amp; G2 Reviews</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs#accountability`}><i class="fi fi-rr-marker mi"></i>Global Presence</a></li>
        </ul></div>
        <div class="mega-col promo span2">
          <span class="label"><span class="idx"><i class="fi fi-rr-badge-check"></i></span> Since 2006</span>
          <h3>Enterprise software with US/EU accountability and global engineering scale.</h3>
          <p class="mega-p">ISO 27001 certified · Clutch 4.9/5 · Offices in USA, Europe &amp; India · 98% client retention.</p>
          <a href={`${BASE}/why-biztechcs`} class="link-arrow">See why 200+ companies trust us <i class="fi fi-rr-arrow-right"></i></a>
