          <li><a href={`${BASE}/resources`}><i class="fi fi-rr-envelope mi"></i>Newsletter</a></li>
        </ul></div>
        <div class="mega-col"><h4>Tools &amp; Downloads</h4><ul>
          <li><a href="#resources"><i class="fi fi-rr-scale mi"></i>Technology Comparison Guides</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${BASE}/roi-calculator`}><i class="fi fi-rr-calculator mi"></i>ROI Calculator</a></li>
          <li><a href="#resources"><i class="fi fi-rr-checkbox mi"></i>Project Estimation Checklist</a></li>
        </ul></div>
        <div class="mega-col promo span2">
          <span class="label"><span class="idx"><i class="fi fi-rr-lightbulb-on"></i></span> Featured</span>
          <h3>Insights from 19 years of enterprise software delivery.</h3>
          <p class="mega-p">Technical deep-dives, industry analysis, and practical guides from our senior engineering team.</p>
          <a href="#resources" class="link-arrow">Browse all resources <i class="fi fi-rr-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
